<tr id="L14"><td><a href="#L14">14</a></td><td>BASHIR:  Well maybe he and I can have dessert while you and the Talarian to wile away the afternoon.</td></tr>

<tr id="L15"><td><a href="#L15">15</a></td><td>GARAK:  But it is a very interesting sociological phenomenon, don't you think? For generations now, humankind has had more than enough food and yet you go about your eating as if you were afraid someone was going to come along and snatch away your plate.</td></tr>

