<tr id="L392"><td><a href="#L392">392</a></td><td>GARAK:  You'll forgive me if I reduce the scope of this conversation to something a little more personal, but why was it necessary to kill me and the rest of our former colleagues, in order to embark on this excursion into the Gamma Quadrant?</td></tr>

<tr id="L393"><td><a href="#L393">393</a></td><td>TAIN:  Because, Garak, I don't plan on going back into retirement when this is over. I plan on going back to my old job and my old life.</td></tr>

<tr id="L394"><td><a href="#L394">394</a></td><td>GARAK:  And you were afraid we knew things, things that could be used against you, and so you decided to have us eliminated.</td></tr>

